dcterms:description: The Stanford Large Movie Review Dataset (IMDb) is a binary sentiment dataset comprising 25,000 labeled movie reviews for training, 25,000 labeled reviews for testing, and an additional 50,000 unlabeled reviews for supplementary self-supervised training.
dcterms:title: IMDb review dataset

dcterms:creator: O. Bodenreider
dcterms:description: The UMLS Meta-Thesaurus is a comprehensive and unified collection of nearly 200 biomedical vocabularies, consolidating various lexical variations of terms into single concepts and outlining their interrelationships.
dcterms:title: UMLS Meta-Thesaurus
